This is how to monotonic of l:
  Remember that up is 1
  Remember that down is 1
  Remember that i is 1
  Do this l's length times:
    When i is at most l's length, then:
      Remember that a is item diff of i and 1 in l
      Remember that b is item i in l
      When a is more than b, then:
        Remember that up is 0
      End when
      When a is less than b, then:
        Remember that down is 0
      End when
      Increase i by 1
    End when
  End do
  When up is 1, then:
    The answer is 1
  End when
  When down is 1, then:
    The answer is 1
  End when
  The answer is 0
